<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.10.8">
<l>pukkaṭimaiyiṉā ṟaṉṉaik kaṇṭa mārkkaṇṭēya ṉavaṉai</l>
<l>nakkapirāṉumaṉ ṟuyyakkoṇṭatu nārāyaṇaṉaruḷē</l>
<l>kokkalar taṭantāḻai vēlit tirukkurukū rataṉuṇ</l>
<l>mikka vātippirā ṉiṟka maṟṟait teyvam viḷamputirē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Taking, so that he escaped that day, even the lord who smiled at Mārkaṇḍeya</l>
<l>who had entered [and] seen [him] because of the servantship [is] the grace of Nārāyaṇa.</l>
<l>while the excellent primeval lord stands in Tirukkurukūr with a fence</l>
<l>of mango blossoms [and] broad screwpine, will you speak of anyother god?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
